<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM8.1">
<l>viṇṇīla mēlāppu virittāṟpōl mēkaṅkāḷ</l>
<l>teṇṇīrpāy vēṅkaṭatteṉ tirumālum pōntāṉē</l>
<l>kaṇṇīrkaḷ mulaikkuvaṭṭil tuḷicōrac cōrvēṉai</l>
<l>peṇṇīrmai yīṭaḻikku mitutamakkōr perumaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O clouds that are as if a blue canopy was spread over the sky!</l>
<l>Has my Tirumāl from Veṅkaṭam, where pure water flows, left [along with you]?</l>
<l>Is this—the full destruction of a woman’s nature in me who am exhausted,</l>
<l>as tears trickle down on the peaks of [my] breasts—a great thing for Him?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
